{"tid":1349252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［大家入晒黎討論］有危自有機 成立臨時行政機關","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:07:44.000Z","uid":76600,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c860e7a0a3a752a6c6cb6c6acb193004e738a9dc","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"而家香港既混亂局勢已加劇到歷史性高位。<br />\n人民對政府既不信任，對社會既不安。都係我地成立臨時機關既大好時機。民安隊、臨時立法會、甚至係臨時政府。香港既種種不穩都係我地建立革命既好時機。<br />\n當能夠平定亂世既唔再係政府，能夠出黎平定亂世既就會被人民擁立成新政府。<br />\n我唔知我既諗法正唔正確，希望大家入黎集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n但我相信機會同破綻住住係出現係混亂同不穩既情況。<br />\n<br />\n香港人成日話未係時機，咁呢一刻時機又到未？"},{"pid":"145b765dd763ae6c9149f8271a3d631ceea1d4ce","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"推 入黎討論"},{"pid":"e5c1aa16f18296be8385e09c1aff964701c60691","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2deda3dd9d802e6537a1dd6e69bdf058919e298","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多次"},{"pid":"50f0361fd6bddaa43d8ba72f9121e905a4dc3f51","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不斷升級升級，歷史話我地知最後都要行到呢一步"},{"pid":"dec1b2a0f415a2d5b368de5ddf4a555737ea0612","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3101c6d8242e0d4e975a098881ee26ba7ed68f4a","tid":1349252,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"推多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed7dce0fa